cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses the application of deep neural networks in robotic vision, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The focus is on recognition and classification of objects, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep metric learning is a key aspect of the proposed approach, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of active learning, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
